  <h1>
   audio_pause_all
  </h1>
  With this function you can pause all sounds that are currently playing.
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">audio_pause_all();
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">N/A
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">if keyboard_check_pressed(ord("P"))
{
    global.Pause = !global.Pause;
    if global.Pause
    {
        audio_pause_all();
    }
    else
    {
        audio_resume_all();
    }
}
</code></pre>
  The above code checks for a press of the keyboard key "P" and if it detects one it sets the global variable "Pause" to
  <span>
   true
  </span>
  or false and then either pauses all sounds or restarts all previously paused sounds.
 </body>
